{"tid":1832281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lalisa罕見「無瀏海」現身！粉絲驚呼：不要再遮了","createTime":"2020-01-21T05:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T10:10:42.000Z","uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"52f5877ddbaf64828d315193d8296b199c4816c5","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"Lalisa擁有甜美五官與火辣身材。雖然已經出道三年多、期間也變換過無數次造型，不過卻始終維持「平瀏海」的髮型。她在昨天（20）下午為工作行程前往仁川機場搭機出國，首度以「無瀏海」的髮型公開現身，前所未見的髮型引起粉絲熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/01/21/200121-12576-1-pXPNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F200121-12576-1-pXPNp.jpg&h=a0b827b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗯無瀏海嗯 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcde6c4cd444aba4028f5d8901157b7b2f644581","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/01/21/200121-12576-6-a5i7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F200121-12576-6-a5i7Y.jpg&h=e75752df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天（20）下午現身仁川機場，她這身造型以及身上的肩背包都來自Prada，寬鬆格紋西裝外套，內搭灰色毛衣，將衣襬收入高腰寬襬褲中展現出復古的氛圍。不過最引人注目的，是Lisa首度以無瀏海的側分髮型公開現身，她在發現現場粉絲驚訝的表情時，還以手上的護照害羞地遮住自己的額頭。前所未有的造型也立刻引起網友的熱烈討論，直說「多了一種知性的感覺」、「美女沒有頂不住的髮型」、「太漂亮了」。"},{"pid":"f1a753e37b7e8a0eb39dfc1975a3afad3071f358","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/01/21/200121-12576-7-lA0Ts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F200121-12576-7-lA0Ts.jpg&h=e255fd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首度以無瀏海的髮型公開現身，引起話題討論。"},{"pid":"e0ad0b2564037ce7c66d3202985214b139c4756e","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9AsPv1SCPMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9AsPv1SCPMg&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=a8ee5fb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9AsPv1SCPMg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W8cnrjJl-v4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW8cnrjJl-v4&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=d56dcce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W8cnrjJl-v4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pRMJn5usxVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpRMJn5usxVU&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=ad6e1e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pRMJn5usxVU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HRrvS0HkJLo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHRrvS0HkJLo&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=90860d4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HRrvS0HkJLo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_3NcgE2FvpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_3NcgE2FvpI&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=098e3854\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_3NcgE2FvpI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cUaDuq2N3sI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcUaDuq2N3sI&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=9421c131\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cUaDuq2N3sI</a>"},{"pid":"4ad686df60185dae2eb204f44ba62c1ab5dc3810","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"Lalisa擁有「人間芭比」之稱，除了甜美的五官外，包括「直角肩」、「頭帶腰」以及一雙纖細長腿的絕佳身材都經常造成話題討論，更以超過2800萬粉絲追蹤穩坐韓國女星間社群女王的寶座。"},{"pid":"00ceefb41d26aa651025c3fdd6c56742d39739c5","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"她自出道以來，不管髮色以及髮型如何改變，幾乎始終維持著平瀏海的造型。除此之外，不管舞蹈動作有多大、後面的頭髮已經一團亂，她的瀏海總是能夠維持不動如山。去年BLACKPINK首度登上美國科切拉音樂祭（Coachella）時，更是被美國網友直接稱作「瀏海女」（Girl with the bangs），就連美國人都對於她如何維持瀏海完美狀態感到非常好奇。"},{"pid":"4d120520644d4fc3694164f699a446ec59e5ef15","tid":1832281,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"9b02688505693920e6c84f889c9165374526a210","tid":1832281,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"學識講普通話先好講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8371e1f5050e523cca70bfc511874f4bbb673984","tid":1832281,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"可愛教主"},{"pid":"df93107fdebed90a3317a73a8e1ed0177ea7a022","tid":1832281,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"想彈她個額頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"cf1269a3be385fbfc896f1efe47569c30a60ce24","tid":1832281,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"blink們點睇新造型 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實除左佢，以往一直瀏住海出道嗰幾位上年都已經露左額，佢應該係最後一個 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE